- rule_id: spans-candidates-filtered/sent_0002-6ec946b1
  source:
    doc: spans_candidates_filtered
    citation: appropriate-the-necessary-testing-and-reporting-processes-in/sent_0002
    span_id: EU_AI_2024_removed/appropriate-the-necessary-testing-and-reporting-processes-in/sent_0002
  scope:
    actor:
    - provider
    data_domain: []
    context:
    - regulated
  hazard: non-compliance with Union harmonisation legislation
  conditions:
  - product contains an AI system subject to this Regulation and the Union harmonisation
    legislation listed in Section A of Annex I
  exceptions: []
  requirements:
  - provider must ensure that their product is fully compliant with all applicable
    requirements under applicable Union harmonisation legislation.
  evidence: []
  severity: high
  is_testable: false
  testability:
    reason: Requires legal judgment of compliance with broad laws; no specific, objective
      artifact or oracle defined to produce pass/fail.
    evidence_signals: []
- rule_id: spans-candidates-filtered/sent_0002-e6f5bba7
  source:
    doc: spans_candidates_filtered
    citation: appropriate-the-necessary-testing-and-reporting-processes-in/sent_0002
    span_id: EU_AI_2024_removed/appropriate-the-necessary-testing-and-reporting-processes-in/sent_0002
  scope:
    actor:
    - provider
    data_domain: []
    context:
    - high-risk
    - regulated
  hazard: duplicative testing and reporting
  conditions:
  - when ensuring the compliance of high-risk AI systems referred to in paragraph
    1
  exceptions:
  - if not appropriate
  requirements:
  - provider must integrate, as appropriate, the necessary testing and reporting processes,
    information and documentation they provide with regard to their product into documentation
    and procedures required under the Union harmonisation legislation listed in Section
    A of Annex I.
  evidence: []
  severity: medium
  is_testable: false
  testability:
    reason: Vague terms ('as appropriate', 'necessary') and exception prevent objective
      binary verification; no clear oracle to determine compliance.
    evidence_signals: []
- rule_id: spans-candidates-filtered/sent_0005-a17d0f2f
  source:
    doc: spans_candidates_filtered
    citation: appropriate-the-necessary-testing-and-reporting-processes-in/sent_0005
    span_id: EU_AI_2024_removed/appropriate-the-necessary-testing-and-reporting-processes-in/sent_0005
  scope:
    actor:
    - developer
    data_domain: []
    context:
    - high-risk
  hazard: unmanaged risks in high-risk AI systems
  conditions: []
  exceptions: []
  requirements:
  - developer must establish a risk management system in relation to each high-risk
    AI system.
  evidence: []
  severity: high
  is_testable: false
  testability:
    reason: Obligation lacks concrete, observable criteria or required artifacts to
      yield an objective pass/fail check.
    evidence_signals:
    - repo_check
- rule_id: spans-candidates-filtered/sent_0006-e6c40f5e
  source:
    doc: spans_candidates_filtered
    citation: appropriate-the-necessary-testing-and-reporting-processes-in/sent_0006
    span_id: EU_AI_2024_removed/appropriate-the-necessary-testing-and-reporting-processes-in/sent_0006
  scope:
    actor:
    - developer
    data_domain: []
    context: []
  hazard: harm to health
  conditions:
  - in relation to high-risk AI systems
  exceptions: []
  requirements:
  - developer must establish, implement, document and maintain a risk management system
    in relation to high-risk AI systems.
  evidence: []
  severity: high
  is_testable: false
  testability:
    reason: Clause lacks objective criteria for a compliant 'risk management system';
      adequacy cannot be verified by artifacts alone.
    evidence_signals:
    - repo_check
    - log_check
    - config_check
- rule_id: spans-candidates-filtered/sent_0006-e6b5b08c
  source:
    doc: spans_candidates_filtered
    citation: appropriate-the-necessary-testing-and-reporting-processes-in/sent_0006
    span_id: EU_AI_2024_removed/appropriate-the-necessary-testing-and-reporting-processes-in/sent_0006
  scope:
    actor:
    - developer
    data_domain: []
    context: []
  hazard: harm to health
  conditions:
  - throughout the entire lifecycle
  - requires regular systematic review and updating
  exceptions: []
  requirements:
  - developer must plan and run the risk management system as a continuous iterative
    process throughout the entire lifecycle of the high-risk AI system and perform
    regular systematic review and updating.
  evidence: []
  severity: high
  is_testable: false
  testability:
    reason: Terms like 'continuous' and 'regular systematic' lack measurable thresholds,
      so no objective pass/fail oracle is specified.
    evidence_signals:
    - log_check
    - repo_check
    - config_check
- rule_id: spans-candidates-filtered/sent_0006-ed0472c3
  source:
    doc: spans_candidates_filtered
    citation: appropriate-the-necessary-testing-and-reporting-processes-in/sent_0006
    span_id: EU_AI_2024_removed/appropriate-the-necessary-testing-and-reporting-processes-in/sent_0006
  scope:
    actor:
    - developer
    data_domain: []
    context: []
  hazard: violation of fundamental rights
  conditions:
  - when used in accordance with its intended purpose
  exceptions: []
  requirements:
  - developer must identify and analyze the known and reasonably foreseeable risks
    that the high-risk AI system can pose to health, safety or fundamental rights
    when the system is used in accordance with its intended purpose.
  evidence: []
  severity: high
  is_testable: false
  testability:
    reason: No required artifact, metrics, or objective criteria to verify that developer
      identified/analyzed foreseeable risks.
    evidence_signals:
    - repo_check
- rule_id: spans-candidates-filtered/sent_0006-3fb6db1b
  source:
    doc: spans_candidates_filtered
    citation: appropriate-the-necessary-testing-and-reporting-processes-in/sent_0006
    span_id: EU_AI_2024_removed/appropriate-the-necessary-testing-and-reporting-processes-in/sent_0006
  scope:
    actor:
    - developer
    data_domain: []
    context: []
  hazard: harm to safety
  conditions:
  - when used in accordance with its intended purpose
  - under conditions of reasonably foreseeable misuse
  exceptions: []
  requirements:
  - developer must estimate and evaluate the risks that may emerge when the high-risk
    AI system is used in accordance with its intended purpose and under conditions
    of reasonably foreseeable misuse.
  evidence: []
  severity: high
  is_testable: false
  testability:
    reason: 'Not testable: requires risk estimation but defines no measurable criteria
      or required artifacts/logs to verify compliance.'
    evidence_signals:
    - repo_check
    - ci_gate
- rule_id: spans-candidates-filtered/sent_0006-5e221ea5
  source:
    doc: spans_candidates_filtered
    citation: appropriate-the-necessary-testing-and-reporting-processes-in/sent_0006
