    foreseeable misuse
  exceptions: []
  requirements:
  - deployer must ensure human oversight aims to prevent or minimise risks to health
    that may emerge when the high-risk AI system is used in accordance with its intended
    purpose or under conditions of reasonably foreseeable misuse.
