  conditions:
  - when providing the system to the deployer
  - for the purpose of implementing paragraphs 1, 2 and 3
  exceptions: []
  requirements:
  - provider must provide the high-risk AI system to the deployer in such a way that
    natural persons assigned human oversight are enabled to properly understand the
    relevant capacities and limitations and be able to duly monitor its operation,
    including detecting and addressing anomalies, dysfunctions and unexpected performance.
